      "content": "i get what u mean about it being sensitive, but like, in the actual business world, isn't there basically a standard? like if someone goes to a big international summit or a high-end gala, there's usually a certain way people are expected to act and dress so they don't look out of place. can u just give me a baseline of what that \"standard\" looks like? like the most common professional norms that people generally follow in global business centers?",
